data.description: NO HOA!! Located in a prime area near I-35, commuting to work or enjoying the vibrant city life is a breeze. Plus, being within walking distance to UNT makes it a perfect choice for students and faculty. Welcome to your dream home! This adorable 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem is a perfect blend of modern comfort and timeless charm. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by the warmth of the newly painted interior and the gleam of fresh new floors. The first living room is inviting and perfect for hosting gatherings or simply relaxing with your loved ones. A second living room provides additional space for entertainment. The kitchen features brand-new countertops, painted cabinets, and stainless steel appliances. The primary and secondary bathrooms have been completely renovated to offer spa-like experiences. The huge backyard is perfect for hosting barbecues and outdoor recreation. Freshly applied exterior paint gives this home a crisp, clean look, making it truly move-in ready.
